{"tid":2296642,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"痴撚線大陸閪扮香港人","createTime":"2020-11-22T15:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T17:40:09.000Z","uid":282619,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e631a0b4afa24aa533572ca08324eac501cf378c","tid":2296642,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CH5L96eF2IL/?igshid=vl5gsqrjf45q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCH5L96eF2IL%2F%3Figshid%3Dvl5gsqrjf45q&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=e6516a19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCH5L96eF2IL%2F%3Figshid%3Dvl5gsqrjf45q&h=9bacceb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CH5L96eF2IL/?igshid=vl5gsqrjf45q</a><br />\n你都on9，我住咁撚耐都未撚聽過有香港人叫廣東話做粵語<br />\n用中國人嚟綁架我哋？我識講，但我係唔撚講呀，吹尻脹呀<br />\n屌你老母入鄉隨俗識唔撚識呀你呢啲大陸閪，你識講又唔撚講，然後up一大堆藉口<br />\n我返到大陸，非廣東話地區我都會講普通話啦，屌你老母根本唔撚識尊重，仲想入侵我哋地方？<br />\n香港本來文化好多元既，乜人都有，又有客家人，有四川人，乜人都有，但佢哋都會肯去學廣東話<br />\n舊時嗰批新移民仲停留緊喺新移民努力融入社區呢個幻想入面，事實上佢哋而家靠緊人多去改變環境要求我哋就佢<br />\n我哋要企起身！我哋要建立自己既民族！就必須先將大陸既劣質文化、行為、思想清走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要講廣東話，同朋友講，同屋企人講，同街外人講，喺香港見到既華人我都要講"},{"pid":"f867af4604d9ae729ffa678ac2f4125b43bb18c2","tid":2296642,"uid":254967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:30:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ac386b38215ed55808f01653364b752980db34e","tid":2296642,"uid":252920,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:32:23.000Z","msg":"對波幾大, 想屌, 去邊度搵佢, 1q 幾錢"},{"pid":"304a6e1f150d65a3b273401d12f5a8838cd5017f","tid":2296642,"uid":316751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意啊 quit香港囉"},{"pid":"67569f6d75dabf65f573d2ab8d2da8dfd083afb6","tid":2296642,"uid":54681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"先唔講普通話唔係我哋自願要學嘅<br />\n<br />\n四川 甘肅 成都 嗰班垃圾成口鄉音<br />\n<br />\n佢哋啲普通話算唔算標準？仲係唔係中國人？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de821a235abeee6681baa2e05b3803fb2d8f2147","tid":2296642,"uid":235501,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"真係有必要分開舊個批新移民同新個班蝗，人地舊個啲真係生活到同香港人一樣，識啲03 04年細細個就嚟香港嘅新移民，佢地連普通話都唔識講，淨係識英文同廣東話，依加個批就調轉。"},{"pid":"172a952ea1554b74d2310b36e8bc03a20b3c566c","tid":2296642,"uid":33749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:42:39.000Z","msg":"以佢邏輯<br />\n以前英屬香港係咪所有人都要識英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d021a4ce33586a4cf43211584dcc827d0f830df2","tid":2296642,"uid":33749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67569f6d75dabf65f573d2ab8d2da8dfd083afb6","tid":2296642,"uid":54681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"先唔講普通話唔係我哋自願要學嘅<br />\n<br />\n四川 甘肅 成都 嗰班垃圾成口鄉音<br />\n<br />\n佢哋啲普通話算唔算標準？仲係唔係中國人？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:44:07.000Z","msg":"唔駛咁遠去到四川甘肅<br />\n近近地廣東都好多人唔識講啦<br />\n小粉紅世界觀狹隘都算<br />\n連自己地方都唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8128291d58897c318948f87e198e4cb9ecc25c71","tid":2296642,"uid":183844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:44:38.000Z","msg":"英文係國際語言<br />\n香港兩文之一添<br />\n要成功比起只面向支那<br />\n是否該學習連中國人都要學習嘅英文好啲呢？<br />\n既然係咁點解佢唔係推崇英文而只推廣支那話呢？<br />\n睇波都係睇到咩上海申花<br />\n點解唔叫中國上海申花？"},{"pid":"f57e3ada3480cf9747a531